{"tid":293711,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"搵奇洛李維斯演一個教病人走出心理陰影嘅醫生係咩玩法?","createTime":"2017-06-22T11:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T05:05:29.000Z","uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0800b1854539d7e744b8f544748fccc8398702c","tid":293711,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"Netflix 今年初在日舞影展買下多部電影的發行權，其中包括美國劇情片評審團大獎《無處為家》（I Don&rsquo;t Feel At Home In This World Anymore）、《灼沙》（Burning Sands）、世界紀錄片觀眾票選獎《黃之鋒：熱血少年 vs. 超級強權》（Joshua: Teenager vs. Superpower）等都已經陸續上架，接下來即將上線的《深刻入骨》（To the Bone）也釋出了首支預告。<br />\n<br />\n此片是美國女導演瑪緹諾松（Marti Noxon）的首部長片電影，並且親自擔綱編劇，內容描述 20 歲的艾倫花了絕大部分的青春時光在對抗厭食症，在被家人送往團體家屋後，透過一名非傳統醫師的治療以及同儕的影響，她開始正視自己的問題，並對抗心魔。<br />\n<br />\n《深刻入骨》演出卡司包括莉莉柯林斯（Lily Collins）、基努李維（Keanu Reeves）、莉莉泰勒（Lili Taylor）、凱莉普雷斯頓（Carrie Preston）等，將在 7 月 14 日全球上線。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7OWWTByPYKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7OWWTByPYKo&d=bg4WwxFL4h8rV85dI2MhqsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=152305f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7OWWTByPYKo</a>"},{"pid":"8a6d6a4c235082d0f720db4b02165a1f542b617c","tid":293711,"uid":48295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"咁先係做戲"},{"pid":"2d68913f4e19820ba9350e7d1a97630799b23eae","tid":293711,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:36:05.000Z","msg":"演返自己"},{"pid":"e7dc80fea08a4df81440dc64b712c8c1db30a826","tid":293711,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"佢咩都經歷過先有資格 唔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bdd610a7ad9a3de5c300bafa22e93ecdb5b7f9","tid":293711,"uid":90315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"題外話，推介大家睇下I Don&rsquo;t Feel At Home In This World Anymore<br />\n有d coen bros vibe <img s